extends layout
append content
    #ProgressiveEnhancement( style="display: none" )
        h5 Choice Screening does not support the browser version you are using. Please use another browser:
            ul
                li
                    a(href='https://www.google.com/chrome') Upgrade to Google Chrome
                li
                    a(href='http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/') Upgrade to Firefox
    #Content( style="display: none" )
        p Welcome, you have been invited by your potential employer/contractor to provide information to Choice Screening for the purpose of conducting a background check.
        ul.welcome-points
            li By completing the following steps you will be providing consent to your potential employer to perform a background check. Completing the information does not mean a background check will be performed.
            li Before submitting youâ€™re information, you will be advised of your rights under federal and state laws, which govern background screening for employment purposes.
            li Information reported on your background check cannot be used to adversely affect your employment without providing you the opportunity to contest the accuracy of the report.
            li The information you provide is confidential and will only be delivered to the clearly specified recipient(s) listed on the background check consent form.
        p Please have the following information ready before filling out the online consent form.
        ul.welcome-points
            li Full Legal Name, Date of Birth, and Social Security Number
            li Past Address History for the Last Seven Years.
            li Employment History: Company Name, Office Location, and Contact information
            li Education History: School Locations, Major, Degree, and Year of Graduation.
        p For verification purposes, please enter in the invitation code you were provided below, and click [Start].
        div.invitation-container
            form.form-horizontal(method='POST', action='/')
                div.control-group
                    strong#invitationLabel.control-label.invitation-label Invitation Code
                    div.controls
                        input#activationCode(type="text", name="activationCode")
                        button#startButton.btn.btn-primary(type="submit", style="margin-left: 10px;") Start

                block scripts
                    <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.8.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
                    if (clientBuild === true || clientBuild === "true")
                        <script src="/js/#{version}/home.js"></script>
                    else
                        <script src="/js/home.js"></script>